## API route: invite user

**File:** `app/api/invite/route.js`

```js
// POST /api/invite
// Body: { email: string }
// Uses service role client to call admin.inviteUserByEmail
// Returns: { success: true } or { error: string }
```

This is the only place the service role client touches auth. Validate that the request comes with a valid admin session before firing the invite ‚Äî check the Authorization header using the anon client's `getUser()`.

