## What NOT to do

- Do not make per-row Supabase requests for tap counts ‚Äî fetch counts in the initial query
- Do not call `supabase.auth.admin.*` methods from a Client Component or any client-side code ‚Äî only from the API route
- Do not use `<form>` tags ‚Äî use div + onClick handlers
- Do not install `date-fns`, `moment`, or `dayjs` ‚Äî use `Intl.DateTimeFormat`
- Do not install a debounce library ‚Äî implement with `useRef` timer
- Do not refetch the full table after create/delete/toggle ‚Äî use optimistic local state updates
- Do not show raw Supabase error messages to the user ‚Äî map them to friendly strings
- Do not close the modal immediately on success ‚Äî show the success screen with the URL and NFC Tools instructions first